elem_dict.text: What We DoWe’ve built the world’s first AI-powered test automation platform to help app distributors deliver quality user experiences to their customers. Our platform scales and tests thousands of apps in parallel without the need to code or maintain tests. We automate testing for the most impactful user experiences so that you can publish your apps faster.
